# Claude Code Runtime Data - SENSITIVE FILES
# These files contain credentials, session data, and personal information

# Credentials and auth tokens (NEVER COMMIT)
**/.credentials.json
**/.claude.json
**/.claude.json.backup

# Runtime session data
**/projects/
**/todos/
**/shell-snapshots/
**/logs/
**/statsig/

# Plugin state
**/plugins/

# Account settings.json are Nix build output (regenerated by home-manager switch)
# and embed /nix/store hashes that churn on every toolchain bump, so they stay
# ignored (the account paths are listed in the parent .gitignore). Only the
# web-session file (.claude/settings.json) is tracked.
!.claude/settings.json
!**/mcp.json
!**/CLAUDE.md

# Allow directory structure
!**/agents/
!**/commands/